:: Start
(set: $petName to "")

What is your pet's name?

(input-box: bind $petName, "X", 1, "Enter your pet's name...")

(link-goto: "Continue", "pet-type")

:: pet-type
What kind of pet is $petName?

[[A dog->dog]]
[[A cat->cat]]
[[A fish->fish]]

:: dog
$petName is a great name for a dog. They'll be chasing sticks forever in your memory.

[[The end->end]]

:: cat
$petName is a great name for a cat. Dignified, a little mysterious — as it should be.

[[The end->end]]

:: fish
$petName is a great name for a fish. Small in size, large in legacy.

[[The end->end]]

:: end
Whatever happens, $petName was lucky to have you.
